8&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800\' class=\'thickbox\' title=\'Simple Related Posts\'>Install</a>)</span>\n<p>Simple plugin that will show related posts.</p>\n','no'),(1382,'recently_activated','a:0:{}','yes');
